---
// Call-to-action section component
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white relative overflow-hidden fade-in-on-scroll">
  <!-- Animated Background Elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-white/10 rounded-full animate-float"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-16 right-20 w-24 h-24 bg-orange-400/20 rounded-full animate-float-delayed"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 animate-fadeInUp">
      همین حالا بیمه خودرو خود را تهیه کنید
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-blue-100 animate-fadeInUp" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      تنها با چند کلیک و در کمتر از ۵ دقیقه
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 mb-8 animate-fadeInUp" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
      <button class="bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover-scale">
        شروع کنید
      </button>
      
      <button class="border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover-scale">
        مشاوره رایگان
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-blue-100 animate-fadeInUp" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
      <p>یا با ما تماس بگیرید: <span class="font-bold text-white">۰۲۱-۱۲۳۴۵۶۷۸</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px) scale(1) rotate(0deg);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-30px) scale(1.2) rotate(180deg);
    }
  }

  @keyframes float-delayed {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px) translateX(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(30px) translateX(20px);
    }
  }

  .animate-float {
    animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .animate-float-delayed {
    animation: float-delayed 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hover-scale:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
</style> 